# 命令参考

所有命令从项目根目录执行。

## 安装与质量

```bash
uv sync --all-groups
uv run ruff check .
uv run ruff format --check .
uv run ty check
uv run pytest
```

## 项目 CLI

```bash
uv run [[ project_slug ]] server run --host 0.0.0.0 --port [[ backend_port ]]
uv run [[ project_slug ]] server run --reload
uv run [[ project_slug ]] server routes
```
[% if database == "postgresql" %]

## Database

```bash
uv run [[ project_slug ]] db init
uv run [[ project_slug ]] db migrate --message "describe change"
uv run [[ project_slug ]] db upgrade
uv run [[ project_slug ]] db downgrade
uv run [[ project_slug ]] db current
uv run [[ project_slug ]] db history
```
[% endif %][% if background_tasks == "taskiq" %]

## Taskiq

```bash
uv run [[ project_slug ]] taskiq worker
uv run [[ project_slug ]] taskiq worker --workers 4
uv run [[ project_slug ]] taskiq worker --reload
uv run [[ project_slug ]] taskiq scheduler
```
[% endif %][% if enable_docker %]

## Docker Compose

```bash
docker compose -f deploy/compose.yaml config
docker compose -f deploy/compose.yaml up --build
docker compose -f deploy/compose.dev.yaml up --build
docker compose -f deploy/compose.prod.yaml up -d --build
docker compose -f deploy/compose.prod.yaml logs -f app
docker compose -f deploy/compose.prod.yaml down
```
[% endif %]
